TITLE: Initializing gqlgen Project Skeleton - Shell
DESCRIPTION: Initializes the recommended gqlgen project structure using the gqlgen CLI. This command generates configuration files, schema, model stubs, and entry point code, setting up the environment for further development. Requires 'gqlgen' to be installed as a dependency.
SOURCE: https://github.com/99designs/gqlgen/blob/master/docs/content/getting-started.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
go run github.com/99designs/gqlgen init
```

