TITLE: Marking GraphQL Field as Explicit Resolver in gqlgen.yml - YAML
DESCRIPTION: This config snippet forces gqlgen to generate a resolver for the 'friends' field on the User type. Used when retaining generated models but customizing field fetching. Dependency: GraphQL schema with friends field present. Output: A method in the generated resolvers. Limitation: Requires manual implementation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/99designs/gqlgen/blob/master/docs/content/_introduction.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
models:
  User:
    fields:
      friends:
        resolver: true # force a resolver to be generated
```

