DESCRIPTION: Defines a repeatable GraphQL directive @goExtraField with arguments to specify additional Go fields directly within the GraphQL schema definition. This directive allows fields like name, type, overrideTags, and description to be specified inline on OBJECT or INPUT_OBJECT types enabling embedding Go-specific extra fields without editing gqlgen.yaml.
