TITLE: Binding Enums via GraphQL Directives in gqlgen
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates defining `@goModel` and `@goEnum` directives to bind GraphQL enum values to specific Go model enums and constants. It maps GraphQL enum fields to Go types and constants, facilitating seamless data conversions between schema and application layer.
SOURCE: https://github.com/99designs/gqlgen/blob/master/docs/content/recipes/enum.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: GraphQL
