TITLE: GraphQL Schema: Multiple File Upload
DESCRIPTION: Defines the GraphQL schema for multiple file uploads. It includes the `Upload` scalar, `File` type for the response, and `UploadFile` input type for the request. The `Mutation` has a `multipleUpload` field that accepts an array of `UploadFile`.
