TITLE: Explicit resolver configuration for nested fields
DESCRIPTION: YAML snippet specifying that the friends field in User requires a resolver, enabling lazy loading or custom data fetching logic. This facilitates fine-grained control over data retrieval, especially for recursive or nested associations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/99designs/gqlgen/blob/master/README.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: YAML
CODE:
```
# gqlgen.yml
models:
  User:
    fields:
      friends:
        resolver: true
```

