TITLE: GraphQL schema for error example
DESCRIPTION: This GraphQL schema defines the structure for an example demonstrating error handling during scalar unmarshalling. It includes an `Email` scalar and a nested input type.
SOURCE: https://github.com/99designs/gqlgen/blob/master/docs/content/reference/scalars.md#_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
extend type Mutation{
    updateUser(userInput: UserInput!): User!
}

input UserInput {
    name: String!
    primaryContactDetails: ContactDetailsInput!
    secondaryContactDetails: ContactDetailsInput!
}

scalar Email

input ContactDetailsInput {
    email: Email!
}
```

